A chaotic Discord bot featuring targeted censorship, random insults,
leaderboards, gambling commands, and pure gremlin energy.

- Dynamic user targeting
- Word censorship system
- Censorship leaderboard
- Random insult generator
- Coin flip & D20 commands
- Voice channel support
- Slash command support

/target @user
/untarget @user
/censored
/whoistheproblem
/insult
/coinflip
/d20
/join
/leave

AI functionality is currently disabled by default.

To enable:
1. Add an OpenAI API key to .env
2. Uncomment the AI command handlers in Bot.js and or deploy-commands.js
3. Restart the bot

Environment Variables
into .env file

DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=your_token_here
CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here


If uploading to GitHub


Before uploading your bot to GitHub:

1. Create a .gitignore file
2. Add the following:

.env
node_modules

3. NEVER upload your .env file
4. NEVER share your Discord bot token
5. NEVER share API keys publicly

If your token is ever leaked:
Go to the Discord Developer Portal and reset the bot token immediately.